{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"4e89ba1f04","title":"右派言论——攻击党、反对党的领导","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"e8b18d8d4c","index":0,"year":1957,"month":5,"day":null,"articleId":"4e89ba1f04"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"4082fe5977","name":"宋宗年"},{"id":"6c72d91291","name":"河南农学院"},{"id":"869ce37c89","name":"赵芹璜"},{"id":"bcd33ba6ce","name":"唐厥旺"},{"id":"e7333bdbef","name":"王国瑞"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"af1b4b35c8","type":"title","text":"右派言论——攻击党、反对党的领导","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4e89ba1f04"},{"id":"969a2796c4","type":"authors","text":"河南农学院唐厥旺赵芹璜王国瑞宋宗年","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4e89ba1f04"},{"id":"0d6edc6248","type":"paragraph","text":"唐厥旺（理化教研组助教）：","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4e89ba1f04"},{"id":"5e5656abea","type":"paragraph","text":"要不是共产党来、要不是土地改革，我也不会遇到困难，所以我仇视共产党、反对土地改革。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4e89ba1f04"},{"id":"1d515e464f","type":"paragraph","text":"赵芹璜（辅教人员）：","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4e89ba1f04"},{"id":"d644a528f2","type":"paragraph","text":"同意民主办校，共产党既不让人说一党专政，又不愿听以党代政，如果不让民主办校，那就一点自由也没有了。党外人士无权，是党的政策造成的。说教授治校不能贯彻党的政策，这是对党外人士的不信任。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4e89ba1f04"},{"id":"868c9671a3","type":"paragraph","text":"国务院就是没有党外人士，储安平说的对。","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4e89ba1f04"},{"id":"cb8b7d2135","type":"paragraph","text":"王国瑞（职员）：","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4e89ba1f04"},{"id":"292456cc69","type":"paragraph","text":"咱院的领导大人是“白脖”（注：指领导不懂教学）怎么能办好学校。工会是党的尾巴，没有原则的跟着党跑。","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4e89ba1f04"},{"id":"c123e848ad","type":"paragraph","text":"宋宗年（电话员）：","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4e89ba1f04"},{"id":"067abc4ad9","type":"paragraph","text":"院领导，对工人是使用打击多，培养教育少。","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4e89ba1f04"},{"id":"088dd23bb6","type":"paragraph","text":" 来源：《右派言论选辑》（河南农学院，1957年12月）。","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4e89ba1f04"}],"page":{"id":"7a0bc8adc0","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4e89ba1f04","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}